title: Capital Organic Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Organic, Juice bar
description: Ovo-lacto vegetarian restaurant with many vegan options, some Goan regional specialties. Semi-outdoor seating with roof top and open walls. Vegan items are not clearly marked on menu, but servers are accommodating for special requests. Fresh juices and smoothies.
streetAddress: Patnem Beach turnoff from Patnem-Palolem coastal road
